Step 1: Kill ALL VS Code processes

Run this in PowerShell (Admin):

taskkill /F /IM code.exe /T
taskkill /F /IM Code.exe /T

Also kill any leftover node processes (important):

taskkill /F /IM node.exe /T
🔥 Step 2: Take ownership (fix permission issues)
takeown /F "$env:USERPROFILE\.vscode" /R /D Y
icacls "$env:USERPROFILE\.vscode" /grant "$env:USERNAME:F" /T
🔥 Step 3: Now delete (should work)
Remove-Item "$env:USERPROFILE\.vscode\extensions" -Recurse -Force
